Class Inventory

    • com.loveboyuan.smarttrader.Inventory

    public class Inventory
extends java.lang.Object
implements Search, java.io.Serializable
    Created by boyuangu on 2015-10-16. Inventory is yet another model class for storing collection info about a particular user; but in contrast to FriendList, it stores all the items a user possesses.
